cs.CV, cs.EM, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper focuses on camera systems and image processing acceleration techniques, which are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The first case study involves energy harvesting, which falls under the category of embedded systems (cs.EM). The second case study involves processing a large amount of data in real-time, which could be categorized as computer architecture (cs.AR) or control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper also discusses video processing, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
